channel.title: What to Bot?
channel.description:
Well I'm working on a Pure WC account. At the moment it is 66 but only has about 10k left till 67.
Now for my question; should I bot Yews or Willows? I know that yews yield more xp and profit, but willows are faster to cut. What would be the fastest way? p.s. it is an f2p acc
